{"type": "article", "id": 22249, "title": "致敬Wes Anderson的沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-15T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130005sAJltpxFwQ2MLH5C.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这套家具系列来自悉尼设计师 Tom Fereday，他利用了家具转折处的数学角度，让它有了拼接的效果。两种沙发的转角都有 120°，可以将三张单人沙发拼成一个圆，或加入两个长沙发拼成椭圆形。其他的沙发或座椅造型方正，都在细的橡木腿上连接软垫，有明亮的颜色和简单的几何感。这套家具的名字“Wes” 是为了致敬美国导演 Wes Anderson（韦斯·安德森，1969年5月1日 －），<a href=\"http://www.tomfereday.com/furniture/wes-range/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130002gQFMxX1avEyIc6Of.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130003vrSbND5xcMCGmLhO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130003QG2Y1yDPT6NdzZRK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130004JOqvICr3GYTwg6jQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130004J5VaiQqXs0BCmWcM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}